  (6, 'An analyst discovers data has missing values that depend on other observed variables. This missingness is:', 'Missing Completely at Random (MCAR)', 'Missing at Random (MAR)', 'Missing Not at Random (MNAR)', 'Complete missingness', 'B', 2, 20),
